#Whisk{} @shallot{1%small}, @garlic{1%clove}, @mayonnaise{1%cup}, @caper berries{2%Tbsp}, @pickles{2%Tbsp}, @chives{1%Tbsp}, @parsley{1%Tbsp}, @lemon juice{1%Tbsp}, @Dijon mustard{1%tsp}, and @whole grain mustard{1%tsp} in a #small bowl{} until combined. Season with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Do Ahead: Tartar sauce can be made 1 week ahead. Cover and chill.
